metadata.name: God is a Black Woman
metadata.description:
Meet Mother Earth of the MetaVerse,
she is the melanin masterpiece of nature
in pure form. Her skin absorbs the suns rays;
darkening her soft skin while filling her with infinite light. 


"Bringing the gifts that my ancestors gave,
I am the dream and the hope of the slave.
I rise, I rise, I rise." Maya Angelou
